OL,3,CWhat is Gatwick's expansion plan and
OL,4,Cwho will pay for it?
OL,6,FGatwick Airport's expansion plan
OL,7,Finvolves bringing its emergency runway
OL,8,Finto routine use.
OL,10,FHere are the answers 14 key questions
OL,11,Fabout the project.
OL,13,F` How many runways does Gatwick have?
OL,15,FIt has one conventional runway and one
OL,16,Fstandby runway.
OL,18,F` What is the standby runway used for?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
