OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782317939
OL,3,CWhat is Gatwick's expansion plan and
OL,4,Cwho will pay for it?
OL,6,FIt is mostly used for aircraft to taxi
OL,7,Fto and from terminals but is also used
OL,8,Fwhen the main runway is closed for
OL,9,Femergencies or maintenance.
OL,11,F` Why does Gatwick want to expand?
OL,13,FIt is the UK's second busiest airport
OL,14,Fand one of the busiest single-runway
OL,15,Fairports in the world.
OL,17,FSpare slots at peak periods are scarce
OL,18,Fand the runway is heavily utilised,
OL,19,Fmeaning disruption can have a severe
OL,20,Fknock-on effect.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
