OL,3,CWhat is Gatwick's expansion plan and
OL,4,Cwho will pay for it?
OL,6,F` What must happen to the standby
OL,7,Frunway for it to be brought into
OL,8,Froutine use?
OL,10,FIt must be moved 12 metres to the
OL,11,Fnorth ` away from the main runway ` to
OL,12,Fmeet strict aviation safety rules.
OL,14,F` What else does the plan involve?
OL,16,FRemodelling and replacing existing
OL,17,Ftaxiways which connect runways to
OL,18,Fterminals, hangars and other
OL,19,Ffacilities, extending both terminals,
OL,20,Fand installing new aircraft gates.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
