OL,3,CWhat is Gatwick's expansion plan and
OL,4,Cwho will pay for it?
OL,6,F` How about transport?
OL,8,FGatwick says it would pay for road
OL,9,Fconnections to both terminals to be
OL,10,Fenhanced, creating fly-overs which
OL,11,Fseparate local traffic from vehicles
OL,12,Ftravelling to or from the airport.
OL,14,FA #250 million upgrade of the
OL,15,Fairport's railway station was
OL,16,Fcompleted in November 2023.
OL,18,F` What would the standby runway be
OL,19,Fused for?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
