OL,3,CWhat is Gatwick's expansion plan and
OL,4,Cwho will pay for it?
OL,6,FDepartures of narrow-bodied planes
OL,7,Fsuch as Airbus A320s and Boeing 737s.
OL,9,F` What impact would that have on
OL,10,FGatwick's capacity for flights?
OL,12,FIt would enable the airport to be used
OL,13,Ffor about 386,000 flights per year,
OL,14,Fabout 100,000 more than current levels.
OL,16,F` How about annual passenger numbers?
OL,18,FThey could rise from about 43 million
OL,19,Fto 75 million by the late 2030s.
OL,21,F` How much will the project cost?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
