OL,3,CWhat is Gatwick's expansion plan and
OL,4,Cwho will pay for it?
OL,6,FGatwick says the plan will cost #2.2
OL,7,Fbillion.
OL,9,F` Who will pay for it?
OL,11,FThe airport says the project will be
OL,12,Fprivately financed. It has pledged to
OL,13,Fmeet the cost without hiking charges
OL,14,Fto airlines.
OL,16,F` When could the new runway open?
OL,18,FIt is hoped flights will take off from
OL,19,Fthe new full runway before 2029.
OL,21,F` Who owns Gatwick Airport?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
