PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782317939
OL,3,CWhat is Gatwick's expansion plan and
OL,4,Cwho will pay for it?
OL,6,FFrench company Vinci and investment
OL,7,Ffund Global Infrastructure Partners.
OL,9,F` Does Heathrow's third runway
OL,10,Fproposal affect Gatwick?
OL,12,FThe Government has indicated its
OL,13,Fsupport for Heathrow's expansion plan.
OL,15,FBut it is likely to be many years
OL,16,Fbefore construction on a third runway
OL,17,Fat the west London airport begins and
OL,18,FGatwick is determined to boost its own
OL,19,Fcapacity ahead of that happening.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
